OL,3,GLondon & South East
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FAny patchy fog will clear
OL,6,Fquickly to give a fine day with plenty
OL,7,Fof sunshine. Generally mild, but
OL,8,Ffeeling cooler towards the east coast
OL,9,Fwith an onshore breeze.
OL,10,
OL,11,CTonight:FMostly clear overnight, with
OL,12,Fa few isolated mist and fog patches
OL,13,Fperhaps developing towards dawn.
OL,14,FBecoming chilly with an isolated rural
OL,15,Ffrost.
OL,16,
OL,17,CThursday:FAny isolated mist and fog
OL,18,Fpatches will soon clear to give
OL,19,Fanother fine and dry day with long
OL,20,Fsunny spells. Mild for most, but
OL,21,Fcooler towards the east coast.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
